ef=\"/docs/getting-started/faq\">FAQ</a></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 mt-5\"><h4 class=\"font-medium sm:text-sm\">Moving Out</h4><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:text-sm dark:text-neutral-300/85 text-neutral-800 ml-0.5\"><a class=\"font-medium text-primary\" href=\"/docs/server-actions/schedule-move-out\">如何安排搬出 - How To Scheule a Move Out</a><a class=\"\" href=\"/docs/server-actions/getToken\">Potential Charges</a><a class=\"\" href=\"/docs/server-actions/getRole\">Security Deposit Refund</a></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 mt-5\"><h4 class=\"font-medium sm:text-sm\">Other</h4><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:text-sm dark:text-neutral-300/85 text-neutral-800 ml-0.5\"><a class=\"\" href=\"/docs/react-hooks/what-to-bring\">需要携带的物品 - What To Bring</a></div></div></div></div></div></aside><div class=\"flex-[4]\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-12\"><div class=\"flex-[3] pt-10\"><div class=\"pb-5\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\"><ol class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 break-words text-sm text-muted-foreground sm:gap-2.5\"><li class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\">Docs</a></li><li role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"[&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right \"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></li><li class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground a\">Server Actions</a></li><li role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"[&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right \"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></li><li class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span role=\"link\" aria-disabled=\"true\" aria-current=\"page\" class=\"font-normal text-foreground b\">Schedule Move Out</span></li></ol></nav></div><div class=\"prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert prose-code:font-code dark:prose-code:bg-neutral-900 dark:prose-pre:bg-neutral-900 prose-code:bg-neutral-100 prose-pre:bg-neutral-100 prose-headings:scroll-m-20 w-[85vw] sm:w-full sm:mx-auto prose-code:text-sm prose-code:leading-6 dark:prose-code:text-white prose-code:text-neutral-800 prose-code:p-1 prose-code:rounded-md prose-pre:border pt-2\"><h1>如何安排搬出 - How to Schedule a Move Out</h1><p class=\"-mt-4 text-muted-foreground text-[16.5px]\">如何在我们的在线门户网站RentVine上安排搬出。</p><div><p>更多信息请点击这里：<a href=\"https://help.rentvine.com/resident-portal-introduction\">居民门户信息</a></p>\n<p>搬出日期由您自己负责。必须在RentVine上在线完成。以下是来自RentVine网站的信息。如果您有具体的日期，搬出日期应在您搬入时添加；如果您按月签订合同，搬出日期应在搬出前30天。除非您的协议中另有规定，我们只在每个月底办理搬出手续：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在这个框中会有一个标有“搬出通知”的框。这是您通知您的物业经理搬出并填写离开原因和转发地址等信息的方式。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/Q9F_VW9Wo-_WrvOGy6WAeQ/82b76841-78de-4710-b69c-4a56f61a3b00/public\" alt=\"搬出图像\" title=\"搬出\"/></p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between sm:py-7 py-5\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 no-underline text-sm px-1\" href=\"/docs/getting-started/faq\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left w-[1.1rem] h-[1.1rem]\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg><p>FAQ</p></a></div><div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 no-underline text-sm px-1\" href=\"/docs/server-actions/getToken\"><p>Potential Charges</p><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-lin